Develop a machine learning model that can predict stock market trends by analyzing multiple data sources including news sentiment, technical indicators, and macroeconomic factors.

Review this 1000-line codebase and identify architectural patterns, potential bugs, performance bottlenecks, and suggest refactoring improvements.
